ve an equal faction hit to a frosty scout. I could be wrong here, i dont have any *hard* evidence <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START ;) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/wink.gif ALT=";)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br><br> <p><table width=640 border=1 bgcolor=#333333 bordercolor=#000000><tr><td width=320 bgcolor=#660000><img src="http://ga.vr9.com/ga-small.gif" align=right><font face="Arial"><font color=#FFFFFF size=+1><b><br><center>Yeonik Shadowclinger</b><br></font><font color=#969696 size=-1>42 Monk<br><a href="http://www.guardianalliance.org" style="text-decoration:none; color: #969696;"><u>Guardian Alliance</u></a><br>Zeb Server</center></font></font></td><td width=320 bgcolor=#660000><img src="http://ga.vr9.com/ga-small.gif" align=right><font face="Arial"><font color=#FFFFFF size=+1><b><br><center>Kanerwei Stonescream</b><br></font><font color=#969696 size=-1>52 Wanderer<br><a href="http://www.guardianalliance.org" style="text-decoration:none; color: #969696;"><u>Guardian Alliance</u></a><br>Zeb Server</center></font></font></td></tr></table></p><i></i></td></tr></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#778899><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub38.ezboard.com/urenalan.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Renalan</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://home.attbi.com/~kwch1/1.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Young Grasshoppah</span><br>  Posts: 20<br> <font color=#8b1a1a>(2/2/02 11:03:59 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fmonklybusiness43508frm2.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=770.topic&index=2>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://home.attbi.com/~kwch1/1.gif WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Getting CoV/Coldain faction</span><hr size=1> Another good idea:<br><br>Check your server's calendar and find out when an uber guild will be doing the 10th ring war..